OL,3,C'Britain's wonkiest road' to be
OL,4,Crepaired two years after landslip
OL,6,FWork to repair a road dubbed
OL,7,F'Britain's wonkiest road' after a huge
OL,8,Flandslip will begin in the summer.
OL,10,FThe B4069 at Lyneham Banks, near
OL,11,FChippenham, was badly damaged the
OL,12,Froad's surface.
OL,14,FParts of the road fell more than 25
OL,15,Fmetres down the hillside and the route
OL,16,Fdeveloped huge cracks with some BMX
OL,17,Friders even using it as a playground -
OL,18,F.
