OL,3,C'Britain's wonkiest road' to be
OL,4,Crepaired two years after landslip
OL,6,FWiltshire Council has now announced it
OL,7,Fhas awarded the contract to rebuild
OL,8,Fthe road, along with drainage works,
OL,9,Fto Octavius Infrastructure Limited.
OL,11,FWork is due to begin in the summer of
OL,12,F2024 and the road is expected to be
OL,13,Freopened in spring 2025.
OL,15,FThe council added that once the B4069
OL,16,Fhas reopened, it will be undertaking
OL,17,Frepairs to the roads in the area where
OL,18,Fthere has been an increase to traffic
OL,19,Fbecause of the closure.
