OL,6,FCabinet member for highways Cllr Nick
OL,7,FHolder said: "We're pleased to award
OL,8,FtheJcontract to rebuild the B4069 at
OL,9,FLyneham Banks to Octavius, after what
OL,10,Fhas been aJdifficult time for the
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,F"As well as the build, in its tender,
OL,14,FOctavius committed to providing
OL,15,Fvarious localJsocial benefits,
OL,16,Fincluding a meet the contractor event,
OL,17,Fproject newsletters andJcommunity
OL,18,Flitter picks.
